        "display_label": "The Raven 1-4",
        "selector": {
          "kind": "text_quote",
          "exact": "Once upon a midnight dreary, while I pondered, weak and weary,\nOver many a quaint and curious volume of forgotten lore—\nWhile I nodded, nearly napping, suddenly there came a tapping,\nAs of some one gently rapping, rapping at my chamber door."
